      <num>SEC. 2.66</num>
      <heading>Created; composition</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The police department of the city is hereby created. The department shall consist
               of a chief of police and such other subordinate officers, assistants, deputies and
               employees as the council may deem necessary.</p>
        <p>(Code 1938, Sec. 190; Ord. No. 15.79, 4/9/79.)</p>
      </content>
